#META# documentType: Legal
#META# documentSubtype: Legal: Divorce
#META# writingSupport: paper
#META# writingSupportDetails: fold lines :: pasted into Mirza Khwaja Muhammad’s notebook
#META# writingSupportNotes: 5+6 fold lines, complete, black ink; cut into two fragments by Mirza Khwaja Muhammad.
#META# foldLines: 5+6 fold lines
#META# contentSummary: The parties to this *iqrār* document are a husband and wife who are both of very high social standing. The husband is a senior military official. His wife seems to have brought a grievance that her husband has been neglecting her. She has managed to get her husband to agree to either drop the neglect or give her a divorce. She even managed to receive the delegated authority to request a divorce, which is usually only in the husband 's purview.
#META# dates: The Gregorian calendar: May-June 1195 (1195-05-20 - 1195-06-17)
